main_2534583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 17, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zsa1665702762575.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zsa1665702762575.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zsa1665702762575.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zsa1665702762575\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The SameSite attribute of HTTP cookie can allow users to declare if their cookie\n      should be restricted to a first-party or same-site context. </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__context_w37ab1b5b1_w38ab1b5_w39ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23549e1_d23550e1_d23551e1\">The <code class=\"ph codeph\">SameSite</code> cookie attribute is a\n            relatively new standard. Uniface supports setting it globally for all cookies in a web\n            application in the Tomcat context configuration.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23552e1_d23553e1_d23554e1\">By default, the <code class=\"ph codeph\">SameSite</code> attribute is not enabled for the Tomcat web server that is installed with Uniface for development and testing.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23555e1_d23556e1_d23557e1\">To enable SameSite cookie support, edit the <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface.xml</span> context configuration file:</p>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__li_d11684e1_d11685e1_d11686e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open the file <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">InstallDir</var>/common/tomcat/conf/Catalina/localhost/uniface.xml</span> in a text editor.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__li_d11687e1_d11688e1_d11689e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23558e1_d23559e1_d23560e1\">Edit the <code class=\"ph codeph\">CookieProcessor</code>element in the file and adjust the value as required. For example:</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;Context docBase=\"C:/Program Files/Uniface/Uniface 103/uniface/webapps/uniface\"&gt;\n &lt;CookieProcessor sameSiteCookies=\"Lax\"/&gt;\n &lt;Valve className=\"org.apache.catalina.valves.AccessLogValve\" prefix=\"uniface-\" suffix=\".log\" pattern=\"common\"/&gt;\n&lt;/Context&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23561e1_d23562e1_d23563e1\">This code defines the context container for the Uniface web application and applies the specified attribute globally to all pages in the application.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n<section class=\"section result body required-cleanup-multiple-ol-elements-in-topic-body\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__result_w40ab1b5b5_w41ab1b5_w42ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23564e1_d23565e1_d23566e1\">This <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface.xml</span> context file can\n            serve as an example for configuring your own Uniface web application. If you are using\n            Tomcat 9 or later (or another web server) in a production environment, please consult\n            the web server documentation.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__p_d23567e1_d23568e1_d23569e1\">For more information, consult the following web pages:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__li_d11690e1_d11691e1_d11692e1\">About <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Set-Cookie/SameSite\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SameSite cookies</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zsa1665702762575__li_d11693e1_d11694e1_d11695e1\">Tomcat's <a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-9.0-doc/config/cookie-processor.html\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Cookie Processor Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wjz1665702539674.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$webinfo: Cookie Topics</a><p>Use these topics to set the properties of a cookie and write state information to a cookie.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534583\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Enabling SameSite Cookie value for Web Server Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 17, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The SameSite attribute of HTTP cookie can allow users to declare if their cookie should be restricted to a first-party or same-site context. The SameSite cookie attribute is a relatively new standard. Uniface supports setting it globally for all cookies in a web application in the Tomcat context configuration. By default, the SameSite attribute is not enabled for the Tomcat web server that is installed with Uniface for development and testing. To enable SameSite cookie support, edit the uniface.xml context configuration file: Open the file InstallDir /common/tomcat/conf/Catalina/localhost/uniface.xml in a text editor. Edit the CookieProcessor element in the file and adjust the value as required. For example: <Context docBase=\"C:/Program Files/Uniface/Uniface 103/uniface/webapps/uniface\"> <CookieProcessor sameSiteCookies=\"Lax\"/> <Valve className=\"org.apache.catalina.valves.AccessLogValve\" prefix=\"uniface-\" suffix=\".log\" pattern=\"common\"/> </Context> Copy This code defines the context container for the Uniface web application and applies the specified attribute globally to all pages in the application. This uniface.xml context file can serve as an example for configuring your own Uniface web application. If you are using Tomcat 9 or later (or another web server) in a production environment, please consult the web server documentation. For more information, consult the following web pages: About SameSite cookies Tomcat's Cookie Processor Component Related Links $webinfo: Cookie Topics Use these topics to set the properties of a cookie and write state information to a cookie. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}